value.name: Little Sky
value.overview: Penelope is adamant about achieving her long-held goal of becoming a reputable on-air news reporter. She realizes it's her moment to fully establish herself when she gets a report that the mayor of Little Sky is gone.

value.name: Fallen Love
value.overview: Lan Youyou’s dream of running a tea oil shop takes an unexpected turn when she discovers her rented villa is already occupied by Ji Bai. Forced into an unusual cohabitation, their lives intertwine in a story full of humor, surprises, and hidden agendas.
